<br>For training to be considered mandatory, the following criteria must be met:<br>
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-60_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-61_">A statutory requirement (such as the Health and Safety at Work Act) requires it
